<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10881</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19327</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克和玛拉把罗西推进了一个监狱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19328</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯先生笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在你再也阻止不了我了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把铁门重重地关上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西听到他把门锁了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西思考着思维普斯先生戴着的那个戒指。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38804</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43612</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘他是在用那个戒指控制着大家，我要把那个戒指毁掉。’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43613</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46943</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了看监狱的四周。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50266</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘我可以把那扇门撞碎。’她想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50267</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53878</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>‘但是思维普斯先生会听到的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53879</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我需要想一个可以悄悄溜出去的办法。’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跺了一下脚，想知道这个地板有多硬。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67552</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有办法了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯先生正在仔细观察一块钻石，突然他听到一声巨响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80570</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“火箭女孩儿正在想办法越狱。”他叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80571</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82741</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大家快去守住门。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有的学生们都扔掉手里的工具。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91080</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们全都聚集在监狱的门口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>砰！传来了一阵巨响。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>整个洞穴都在震动。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101016</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“如果火箭女孩儿逃脱出来，就马上抓住她！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯先生命令道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105709</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然间——砰！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108403</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>石头飞散开来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108404</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西从大家身后的地板下蹦了出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>思维普斯先生想躲开，但是他不够快。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>嗞轰！罗西的眼睛里发射出激光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122769</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>戒指爆炸了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124503</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128533</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的戒指！”思维普斯先生叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>瞬间，学生们身上的胸针就失去了光芒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>137652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们这是在哪儿?”杰克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>137653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么事，火箭女孩儿？”玛拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们都被思维普斯先生催眠了。”罗西回答，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148621</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他并不是真的校长，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148622</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152585</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他强迫你们来帮他挖学校地下的钻石。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152586</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没错。”这时，史密斯侦探走了进来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165543</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在，思维普斯就要进监狱了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165544</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169686</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>眨眼之间，火箭女孩儿就消失了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了一会儿，罗西出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她穿着平常的衣服，还有一个星星胸针别在上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179040</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181014</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“发生了什么事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181015</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她装作一副也被催眠过的样子嘟囔道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔满脸怀疑地看了她一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197138</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早晨，潘校长和其他的老师们都回来上班了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197139</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201823</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看上去一切都恢复正常了。”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201824</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204983</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我真高兴。”杰克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210062</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“比起在钻石矿里面干活，我还是更喜欢学习。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210063</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们知道吗？”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215447</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以去动物园了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215448</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我妈妈告诉我，学校现在有足够的钱了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225239</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从哪里来的钱啊？”特勒尔问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225240</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“潘校长要把钻石卖掉！”玛拉说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哇！”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我说过，火箭女孩儿什么都可以解决的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是她帮助我们学校得到了钱。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西什么也没有说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>